            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> lemon pepper free range chicken</strong> with the <strong>sweet potato mash</strong> and the <strong>caramelised</strong> <strong>onion greens </strong>to the side</p><p>Tip: Remove the lemon rounds from the chicken as these will be bitter!</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>gravy </strong>all over and garnish with the <strong>charred lemon wedges</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
